{"tid":2074582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際戰線］ 荷蘭嘅聯署需要你！","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T04:57:52.000Z","uid":15677,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4717ee1cd917f9063138cbfa9a4fa4adccf8ba","tid":2074582,"uid":15677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"Hi 又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際戰線又需要你嘅一分力！<br />\n<br />\n繼上幾次聯署 NL4HK今次又草擬咗一份聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook post : <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/691582370924154/posts/3071752619573772/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F691582370924154%2Fposts%2F3071752619573772%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=257d6d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/691582370924154/posts/3071752619573772/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署： <br />\n<a href=\"https://steunhongkongstopstedenband.petities.nl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteunhongkongstopstedenband.petities.nl%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=5e6ada13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://steunhongkongstopstedenband.petities.nl/</a><br />\n<br />\n(原文按link 睇）<br />\n<br />\nStand with Hong Kong! End the twin city partnership with Beijing &amp; Shenzhen!<br />\nIntroduction<br />\n<br />\nWe / Wij <br />\nResidents of Amsterdam and the Netherlands.<br />\n<br />\nObserve / constateren <br />\n<br />\nThat Amsterdam, the city that embraces liberty and freedom <br />\nThat the government of China increasingly limits freedom of its citizens: systematic abuse of ethnic minorities, repression against religious groups and arbitrary arrests and detention of civil rights defenders.<br />\nThat the latest introduction of National Security Law in Hong Kong will greatly erode the freedom of speech and freedom of press in the region, and is a blatant breach of an international treaty.<br />\n<br />\nUrge / verzoeken <br />\n<br />\nThe mayor and the college of mayor and councillors to end twinning with the two Chinese cities<br />\nAnd to raise the issue in The Hague and within the European Commission. Every EU-China strategy should reflect the core values of the Netherlands and Europe<br />\nAnd to urge The Hague to speak out against oppression by China<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地需要200人嘅簽名 （要係荷蘭住緊先計）<br />\n到時候七一荷蘭會有集會 <br />\n我地會將份聯署交去Amsterdam 嘅市政議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n住緊荷蘭又或者識人住係荷蘭嘅你可以出一分力啦！<br />\n請大大力share 俾其他人 告支那上海牙法庭！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bd338e36d2eef56d0138dc42d8fa48d8d47b907","tid":2074582,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"48a9a157105c702db2627938649dd6d749227833","tid":2074582,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=